menu "XRING LMK"

config XRING_LMK
        tristate "XRING LMK MODULE"
        help
          Choose this option to enable xring lowmemorykiller.
          When the system enters a low memory scenario or user mode
          actively triggers recycling, this module will be called to
          kill the process.

config XRING_LMK_MULIT_KILL
        bool "XRING LMK MULIT KILL ENABLE"
        depends on XRING_LMK
        help
          Choose this option to enable xring lowmemorykiller mulit killer.
          After turning on this function, each killing process will be checked
          and killed according to the multi-kill configuration issued by the user.
          The relevant configurations include the number of killing processes, timeout delay, etc.

endmenu
